{"type": "article", "id": 63650, "title": "再生塑料做的电动车，专为城市通勤而设计｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-05-09T23:15:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 58473, "name": "Mandalaki Studio"}, {"id": 58474, "name": "Estrima"}, {"id": 19566, "name": "Note Design Studio"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 58475, "name": "KAE"}, {"id": 58476, "name": "Allermuir"}, {"id": 48332, "name": "LAYER"}, {"id": 2819, "name": "Marc Newson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190509215441A09UBkXd1PnufDi4.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Birò O2 car by Mandalaki Studio &amp;Estrima</h3><p>Mandalaki Studio 与意大利汽车公司 Estrima 合作设计了由 80％再生塑料制成的电动概念车。</p><p>根据设计团队的说法，Birò O2 是一种电动汽车，其回收塑料的百分比高于市场上任何其他汽车。O2 新款基于最初的 Birò 汽车，一种专为城市通勤而设计的全电动汽车，其紧凑性足以停放在自行车停放区域，且配有可拆卸电池。</p><p>Birò O2 不是用厚而高密度的 ABS 塑料，而是通过将废塑料再循环到无污染的车辆中来为废塑料带来新的生命。</p><p>汽车的所有其他元件，如座椅、转速表、方向盘和车门，都是由各种类型的非再生塑料制成，主要是热成型 PVC。</p><p>此外，该车还拥有强大的电动发动机，最高时速可达 65 公里，每次充电可行驶 100 公里。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215529JvODo4ACeQBFrygK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.798709\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905092155294NxJjazVuo0RwbIK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.763536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215530pRPwvb7i63eDsljV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/05/09/mandalaki-biro-o2-recycled-plastic-concept-car/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>「美术馆」空间套系 by Note Design Studio</h3><p>家居设计品牌造作推出「美术馆」空间套系新品，操刀设计的是瑞典团队 Note Design Studio，着眼都市中等户型面积，灵活辐射紧凑空间和开敞大空间，以“轻设计”、“轻女性”为关键词，在设计元素与空间比例上，适度丰盛兼顾适度空灵，延展出全屋可以观赏，也可以使用，有日常气味的美好设计。</p><p>套系设计灵感来自于美术馆中那些迷人的风景画，提取了油画画框、风景画色彩为核心元素。</p><p>在统一了全系设计语言基础上，3 种色彩的不同组合，带来了不同空间色温的变化。56 款家具适配全屋 5 大主空间，包括客厅、餐厅、卧室以及书房等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g08683e05t0\" allowfullscreen=\"“true”\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215613ehZsEfMtq59PHXm6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598437\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215613jMRPu5W2kYJtXKVm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215613Ux4RucJqK8wgelbZ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215614yF1EuOAM5o4mZvGr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215615rRLM9xqX6jenJ40w.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593229\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905092156199tKR43pxD0W2nOBY.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.626563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Horizon Soft Luggage collection by Marc Newson for Louis Vuitton</h3><p>Louis Vuitton 全新 Horizon 手拉式行李箱系列，由工业设计师 Marc Newson 设计，四轮式手提机舱行李箱非常轻巧，但容量却很大。</p><p>这是 Horizon 系列行李箱的第二代设计 Rolling Duffle。全新系列行李箱的外壳以热塑立体织物构成，以特制弹力线及热熔线等高科技纱线，配合无缝编织技术制成一体成型的无聊，然后会进行防水处理，袋面的口袋及拉链则以超声波切割技术制作。</p><p>在塑造基本箱型的过程中，品牌以热熔胶取代 95% 传统产品所用的缝线，功能性很强，也延续了 Marc Newson 高科技感的设计风格，而表面的双面提花织物点缀以 Marc Newson 演绎的 Louis Vuitton 经典的 Monogram 图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215652him0KpcJSj2NTt4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215652qkvIx36GSszcTPAt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905092156533JBEhXd4YO0WZF9k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215653HTR7OMiAPyDUcKoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215653mODt74gNh9G1ybnR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215654ArFu5VyZefH2YlKm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215654nvZpyCH6JKijuEcz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562183\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>COFFIRE Project by KAE</h3><p>如何给批量化产品带来独特性和较强的识别性，COFFIRE 项目是个值得研究的案例。</p><p>COFFIRE 瓷灯使用回收的咖啡渣作为可持续的着色材料来给注浆翻模而成的陶瓷胚胎进行特殊的熏烧着色处理。通过这种熏烧工艺制作出来的表面纹理和颜色各不相同。自然形成了大理石肌理般的效果，这是任何釉都无法做到的效果。</p><p>这种着色工艺的灵感来源于古老的坑烧技术。瓷表面的咖啡渣在 700-1000℃ 低温烧制着色的过程中，会释放出生物油，糖和盐等化学元素，它们之间相互的氧化作用下，就会在陶瓷表面产生粉色效果。同时由于湿度，浓度和温度的关系，形成了最后大理石般的肌理。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215732ml6DZaLbXpNqU5wM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498958\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215732TOw7ehoP8z3VuX14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215732AB9KxeETg40OZs5n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215732mfs394LYrOVGXotQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215733BOQDr5ZzGcomejqF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215733PHjBXAKJlWZ9bs1d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.zhekaizhangdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KAE</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>AXYL bench by LAYER for Allermuir</h3><p>AXYL 长椅是 LAYER 工作室为英国家具品牌 Allermuir 设计的 AXYL 系列中的新品。</p><p>AXYL 系列以倒置的 Y 型框架为基础，兼顾了高水平的结构完整性和独一无二的设计语言。每款产品都拥有极为流畅的轮廓和衔接细部，使用者可以对产品的饰面、颜色和材质进行混合搭配，以创造多样化的迭代。</p><p>AXYL 长椅是由可循环利用的铸铝框架和胶合木椅身组合而成。模块化的设计使其拥有一系列可互换的配件，包括框架和椅身的颜色、饰面和长度等。另外座位部分还有胶合木板款、扶手款、坐垫款以及全包型软垫款可供选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215815OzrI38l9LtbuSaVB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215815RcMgpkJw3YHAKzjQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.989583\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215816rPk2osW1dN6J7xHG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215816wIOFKclUm6PARs5n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.788542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215816pEl3Jmk1MVNGBi8T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215816y2DM0Gqrngpxoz7P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215817GxyYFhNmsXJKnTlw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215817j1nkuw7JHV8NPBxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215817bgiHljhE5JrUQf9Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215818jQR72Cq09sA6ISPW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215818gu9QOYZsxFqdVbGE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215818yI0EeOHnlXmFkPT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509215818MBspJKXjExczRGwU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.789583\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://layerdesign.com/#top-page\" rel=\"nofollow\">LAYER</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}